text: *Ljupka is a Croatian and Macedonian female given name Those with the name include: *Ljupka Dimitrovska (1946–2016), Croatian-Macedonian singer *Ljupka Gojić (born 1982), Croatian model and the face of Givenchy *Ljupka Džundeva (born 1934), Macedonian film and theater actress Category:Croatian feminine given names
title: Ljupka
